r文件和developer的cer文件，然后对应生成两个provision文件，这中间的步聚可以到苹果官网查看，涉及到app id， in house先择。\n\n<strong>5：程序release版本发布</strong>, 参照官方文档：http://help.apple.com/iosdeployment-apps/mac/1.1/#app43ad871e\n在xcode中发布程序的最后一步，记得钩上下面的选项，会帮你生成文档中所指的描述文件，配置好后，就可以不通过itunes, 苹果认证，无线安装企业级in house应用文件了。\n<a href="http://www.ihakula.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/771b91d8e6d89a290b1621243df59671.png"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-250" title="ih house" src="http://www.ihakula.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/771b91d8e6d89a290b1621243df59671.png" alt="" width="536" height="229" /></a>\n\n6: 参考文档\nhttp://help.apple.com/iosdeployment-apps/mac/1.1/#app43ad871e\nhttp://www.apple.com/business/accelerator/deploy/app-distribution.html\n\n7: Enjoy :)', 'iOS发布 in house 企业级应用, 证书申请，无线安装', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '246-revision', '', '', '2012-11-10 10:49:06', '2012-11-10 02:49:06', '', 246, 'http://www.ihakula.com/uncategorized/246-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
